Class CacheStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.tools.CacheStatsBase
      • gw.api.tools.CacheStatistics
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Deprecated. 
    This class is obsolete and will be removed in the next major release. The current implementation of the cache uses CacheStatisticsSnapshot.

    @Deprecated
public class CacheStatistics
extends CacheStatsBase
implements java.lang.Comparable
    This is a simple class to keep track of the statistics for a cache.
